sentences: John Eric "Jeric" Salvanera Gonzales (born August 7, 1992) is a Filipino actor.
Gonzales joined the Ginoong Laguna 2012 and won 2nd Runner Up.

Also after winning Protégé, Jeric was signed, with Thea Tolentino, to be part of Teen Gen, a sequel of the teen oriented show of the 1990s, T.G.I.S..On 2013, Gonzales appeared as a guest in sitcom Pepito Manaloto.
In 2014, Gonzales became part of the cast of Hustisya and in Nora Aunor's Dementia.
Also in 2014, Gonzales became a member of the musical trio 3logy with Abel Estanislao and Jak Roberto.
Gonzales became part of the now defunct Sunday noontime variety show Party Pilipinas with the other top six finalists.
